{"tid":919264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁國雄：如果你將伍迪希，加曾麗文，加阿基，加李卓人，贏埋添！","createTime":"2018-11-28T02:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T12:58:27.000Z","uid":49388,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"38c5c33c2bc2107d5f04e55e92a66cb67dae65a4","tid":919264,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"無神論者巴別塔 fb:<br />\n<br />\n仇思達節錄咗D100版本長毛「鎅票論」新譯：<br />\n<br />\n「搵所謂鎅票嚟削弱你，跟住搵幾個普通人出嚟拉多你千零票，個設計好準嘞。如果你將伍迪希，加曾麗文，加阿基，加李卓人，贏埋添！」（D100，2018年11月27日）<br />\n<br />\n又等我節錄花膠台版本嘅長毛「鎅票論」：<br />\n<br />\n「所謂鎅票，就係響你無勝算之下仍然堅持參選令到他人不參選，除非你話我聽，你係諗住會贏倒！」（花膠台，2018年11月27日）<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，有邊個人出黎選唔會同人講自己有信心會贏架（最多話選情唔樂觀），馮檢基由參選果刻去到開票前一刻，次次都講到明覺得自己有機會贏架！咁依你定義，馮檢基點會係鎅票？<br />\n<br />\n除非你長毛判斷倒參選嘅人其實係講大話，內心從來都想鎅票啦。但如果你真係有資格判斷，咁選舉主任又點解無資格判斷本土自決派參選人係咪誠心相信自己反港獨自決呢？咁誅心咁你同共產黨有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n但都未到最激果Part，最尾佢將所有陳凱欣同李卓人以外嘅參選人，話「全面客觀效果都係拎走咗啲票」，即係響長毛心目中，除咗飯民同建制大台欽點嘅候選人，全部都唔應該出黎選！其實長毛係咪已經老懵懂到連民主嘅基本理念都唔記得咗？唔通伍迪希出黎選呀陳凱欣又要批評佢出黎鎅票，阿鄧家彪出黎選又要批評方國珊出黎鎅票，阿陳家珮出黎選又要批評馬草泥出黎鎅票？<br />\n<br />\n不過最好笑嘅都仲係，依照長毛定義，咁當日陶君行出黎九東鎅死黃洋達令謝偉俊當選；黃浩鉻出黎新西鎅死李卓人令何君堯當選；吳文遠出選大南區鎅死陳文佑令莊永燦當選（仲未計金鷹都有份出黎鎅票），咁你長毛係咪要為社民連歷年鎅票往跡道歉先？抑或佢地覺得自己有機會贏就唔係鎅，馮檢基覺得自己有機會贏就係鎅票任你定義？<br />\n<br />\n當然，到你唔出黎選，好似黃毓民咁，又會比長毛屌話佢縮埋響個網台唔出嵿，又會比佢問除咗響網上打飛機之外仲做過啲乜，即係無論你做乜，都總會搬到龍門可以比佢射入網&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/videos/2097381997241780/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenryporterbabel%2Fvideos%2F2097381997241780%2F&d=E1T%2B3%2Fwi7mooJkZ6DPK9TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=60f6f391\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/videos/2097381997241780/</a>"},{"pid":"e986d8086467011370904e40c3d568f267c1999f","tid":919264,"uid":49643,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:10:33.000Z","msg":"以前果個長毛去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018299dcc1721cdd3ef2d3719c544a5f134a84b5","tid":919264,"uid":24824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"唉 長毛 變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06aac4c1d4c708f428b981217f7e53473dbd4ad","tid":919264,"uid":61280,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢隻毛主席比毛主席更毛主席，&quot;錯在他們！！1&quot;</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6956d975e35d62895b9c9480d56aa7f7a5379e1b","tid":919264,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"佢痴左線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3ec88bdb17235f7420752b4b19e0c783126709","tid":919264,"uid":54721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"加埋陳凱欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d5adfb1efe55ced729b0657ed852e847c90011","tid":919264,"uid":31215,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"點解要屌其他人<br />\n唔檢討下自己嘅策略呢<br />\n<br />\n泛民形象插水<br />\n得返啲深黃絲<br />\n本土唔賣賬<br />\n先係死亡主因<br />\n<br />\n你係有料到<br />\n驚咩人𠝹票<br />\n自己廢，任何人參選都打擊到自己，就唔俾人參加，迫人喺兩舊屎含淚揀件冇咁臭，而唔係整好自己<br />\n呢啲係乜撚策略？"},{"pid":"5cdfdb3db9ffd957983ab331602fa646b09751ce","tid":919264,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3ec88bdb17235f7420752b4b19e0c783126709","tid":919264,"uid":54721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"加埋陳凱欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"係呀，李卓人嘅票本身有200k up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008502e24c0fb26e1faf9b3530a51f718450e974","tid":919264,"uid":26672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"諗起毓民，話陳健康都𠝹鳩人哥票，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係輸比冇投票/無效票嗰班啊，人地唔想投比你啊，仲唔自省喺度屌票，嗰頭李卓人話要同本土派合作，轉個頭長毛又繼續屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我buy毓民，你咁搞法新東都可能輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7909dd20f92c0f69c4e74c3f4a5d6b65b9209c","tid":919264,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"一黨專政咪無鎅票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8135b2d87c49c79a45ffe042e12d956133f4e8","tid":919264,"uid":45148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實你搵楊惡橋，梁天琦出黎選贏左添</span><br />\n<br />\n李卓人d人講得無錯<br />\n支聯會色彩太大<br />\n建樹又無乜"},{"pid":"a993b7f84e117ecac66bc4152e687b71f86932d7","tid":919264,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">扮民尤其毛狗呢隻僭共諜，先屌爆自己點解既然你地鳩吹李老人係天命所歸，何不就快快趣幾個鐘初選KO收錢機呢？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句到尾，你地成班民演根本同你地好多幕後老闆共狗一鳩樣，一面話港獨極少數，一面心照就話&quot;自決&quot;等如&quot;港獨&quot;囉仆街！！！</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"08008a1f155a61e8ba4788e5cd791983b27c5133","tid":919264,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d555c295d9f340c1943e3b5dbcad39fcaee812c","tid":919264,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"仲痴線過司徒老賊"},{"pid":"901f5104d2e00399e07660e85cf21c9e74746a37","tid":919264,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲痴線過司徒老賊</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根撚本支徒華，佢同成班匯點都係共諜，只不過唔係跟揸緊大權個乍字頭而已！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d08812f4f23c1f48226ba67e326290b61fa2e3","tid":919264,"uid":197364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！食過橋米粉啦！出嚟表演屙爛屎啊！出嚟選啦！嘥時間！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長毛完美示範咩叫回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d290ed36b8ab5b025a63b23df4ea356ee5f848","tid":919264,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一黨專政咪無鎅票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fa55a755f729e2f77674d5a6c54fed1709979c","tid":919264,"uid":200903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"喂阿哥 收啦 你04年係咪鎅走鑽石名單嘅票令中間超人落選呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEBjcER.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEBjcER.png&h=07610cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec6d5